Fixed: MOTD is correct when it is reshown
Fixed: Music plays correctly on big endian machines (e.g. PPC macs)
Fixed: Chat tooltips have been moved out the way
Fixed: Bilboard aspect ratios in camera mode

Added: Tooltips are split into two catagories (info and help) each of which can be disabled
Added: Rules tab shows options changed for this level(L) and options changed from default(*)

